🌱 Plant Hormones (Quick Symbols)
Auxins → ↑Leaves + ↑Roots + bends to light 🌞 → Stretch & Reach
Cytokinins → ↑Shoots + ↑Branching + leaf longevity 🍃 → Growth Booster
Gibberellins → ↑Stem length + ↑Seed sprout + proper leaf orientation 🌿 → Tall & Strong
ABA → Stress (drought/cold) → ↓Growth + closes pores 💧 → Stress & Survival
Ethylene → Ripening 🍎 + leaf aging 🍂 + stress signal ⚠ → Ripen & Age
Brassinosteroids → ↑Strength + stress resilience 💪 → Strength & Vigor
Jasmonates → Pest & disease defense 🛡 + temporary ↓Growth → Bodyguard
Salicylic Acid → Immune/stress defense 🦠 → Immune System

Combinations:
Auxins + Cytokinins → Big leaves & fast growth 🍃⚡
Gibberellins → Strong stems & proper leaf orientation 🌿💪
ABA + Ethylene → Slow growth / dormancy ⏸
Brassinosteroids → Resilient leaves 🍂💪
Jasmonates + Salicylic Acid → Pest protection 🛡🦠
🌡️ Nepal Seasons → Plant Growth → Hormones → Care

Spring (Mar–May):
18–30°C / 8–15°C 🌤 → Humidity moderate 💧 → Auxins + Cytokinins →
Leaves ↑ + Stems ↑ + Roots ↑ + Babies ↑ →
Care: Bright indirect light 🌞, moist soil 💦, encourage rooting 🌱

Summer / Monsoon (Jun–Aug):
25–32°C / 15–24°C 🌦 → Humidity high 💦💦 → Gibberellins + Auxins →
Leaves ↑↑ + Stems ↑↑ + Soil & Aerial Roots ↑↑ + Babies ↑↑ →
Care: Support climbers 🪜, watch rot ⚠, propagate if needed ✂

Autumn (Sep–Nov):
18–25°C / 10–18°C 🍂 → Humidity moderate 💧 → ABA ↑ + Ethylene →
Growth ↓ + Variegation stabilizes 🎨 + Roots slow ↓ + Babies slow ↓ →
Care: Reduce water 💧⬇, avoid disturbing roots/babies ✋

Winter (Dec–Feb):
12–22°C / 2–12°C ❄ → Humidity low-moderate 💧 → ABA + Ethylene →
Dormancy ⏸ + Leaves age 🍂 + Roots dormant 🛌 + Babies dormant 💤 →
Care: Avoid overwatering 💦❌, bright indirect light 🌞, protect from cold 🧣

🌿 Aroids vs Philodendrons (Growth Symbols)

Aroids:
Climber/Upright 🧗 + Large/Fenestrated leaves 🍃 + Slow variegated growth 🎨⬇ + Strong aerial roots 🌱💪 → Support + careful watering 💧

Philodendrons:
Climber/Trailing 🌿 + Heart/Elongated leaves ❤️ + Fast variegated growth 🎨⚡ + Soft roots 🌱 → Bright indirect light 🌞 + Easy propagation ✂

Seasonal Shortcut Symbols:

Spring → Leaves ↑ + Roots ↑ + Babies ↑ (Philodendron faster ⚡)
Summer → Leaves ↑↑ + Aerial Roots ↑↑ → Watch rot ⚠
Autumn → Growth ↓ + Variegation stabilizes 🎨
Winter → Growth ↓↓ + Dormancy ⏸ + Babies dormant 💤
⚡ Variegation Note

White / chimeric cells ⚪ → No chlorophyll → Photosynthesis ↓ → Growth slower than full-green Philodendrons 🍃⬇


